{
  "stem": "2718.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't say they wanted to-- wanted to kill the Jews, but they wanted to get rid of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whatever there was wrong in the country, whatever-- whatever there was any-- any misfortune, or-- everything was-- the Jews were blamed for everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The economy was down, the-- if it was hailing, it was the Jews who ordered it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, I'm just saying it as an example.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- but when it came to those people-- and these people were the ones who after it was carried, all the atrocities, when the time came, the Germans did not need any-- they didn't need to encourage them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't need to worry about it that it won't be carried out as good as they would be doing it, because it was all the orders and all the plans were carried out far better than the Germans could have every dreamed it, without the Germans being involved.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Germans were not involved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On the contrary, Germans were more-- more humane than the Hungarians were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yep.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yep.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the favorite slogan, Jews go back to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, we-- we just took it as-- as-- how do you take people who-- who-- who want to harm you or want to get rid of you?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or-- we took them as they would be jealous because Jews in general were-- were well off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were plenty of-- there were [INAUDIBLE] of Jews who were not well off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But only-- only the people, only the Jews who were well off were brought into the sort of the limelight and were made an example, like controlling the economy and-- and-- and taking advantage and-- of the working class and so forth.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
